nodes.text: Marauder was a Warrior-class gunship in the New Republic's Fifth Defense Fleet, captained by Hannser.

The Marauder had been sent to intercept the Teljkon Vagabond as part of Colonel Pakkpekatt's fleet. Some time later, the Marauder aided the Indomitable in eliminating a Yevethan T-type thrustship in the Battle of ILC-905.
